=======================
fy_arena_c17_v1, made by:
Genome.Soldier (aka: Hum4n01dTyph00n)
other credits: Everyone at Valve who made the great area of City 17 for Half Life 2.
======================= 

Description:
This map has some great close quarters urban warfare, so I doubt there will be any sniping on here, unless you can reach one of the spots I added in. I decided to turn part of Half Life 2's City 17 into a Counter-Strike: Source map, so, here it is. This map is still in testing, so if you see any problems, email me or message me at any of the below. Thanks. 

Textures:
I don't believe you guys need any extra textures, but if you do, let me know and I'll get you the ones you need if they aren't showing up.

Legal Agreement:
I don't care, it's my seventh actual completed map, it can be distributed to whomever you wish, BUT, give credit where credit is due, to me (if you do distribute it), and any other credited sources listed above.

Suggestions:
If you have any, please let me know.
